{"tid":690756,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[世紀騙案] 林鄭：樓價飊升治本方法必須增加土地供應","createTime":"2018-06-05T06:23:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T10:24:49.000Z","uid":69289,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"bdfe15524b38b9dd6b04daacf4aaa9c194caf8e6","tid":690756,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:23:47.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2011</div><br />\n立法會十六題：遏抑樓市炒賣措施<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n政府一直密切監察私人住宅物業市場的發展，並對防止資產市場泡沫風險的形成保持警惕。就此，政府時刻勸喻市民在作出置業決定時要小心衡量風險，量力而為。二○一○年二月、四月、八月、十月及十一月，政府循四個方向，包括<span style=\"color: red;\">從根本着手增加土地供應</span>、遏抑物業投機、增加物業交易的透明度以及防止按揭信貸過度擴張，推行了多項措施以確保物業市場健康平穩發展。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201103/16/P201103160144.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201103%2F16%2FP201103160144.htm&d=ReI%2BzhX26GbyCeZBK3HxHWxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=efd07c6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201103/16/P201103160144.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n行政長官在《施政報告》推出新居屋計劃<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n行政長官曾蔭權今日（十月十二日）在《施政報告》中宣布，重新推出居屋計劃，並增加土地供應，為低收入家庭提供有能力購買的住屋。<br />\n<br />\n曾蔭權說：「『安居樂業』是市民的期望，也是政府的願景。」<br />\n<br />\n「對於住屋，政府一向都有承擔。」<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201110/12/P201110120182.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201110%2F12%2FP201110120182.htm&d=ReI%2BzhX26GbyCeZBK3HxHWxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=4362f438\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201110/12/P201110120182.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2012</div><br />\n行政會議非官守議員談財政預算案 <br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n記者：可否談談土地政策？市場預期樓價將會下調，這次增加供應單位對市場會有甚麼影響？市建局參與改建工廈，你怎樣看這個建議？<br />\n<br />\n行政會議非官守議員召集人：土地供應方面，這幾年市民對樓價方面比較擔憂，尤其這兩年樓價升得比較快。<span style=\"color: red;\">政府有新措施出台，無論是印花稅或其他方法，但是增加供應事實上是一個必需的措施。</span>大家住在香港，都想自己住優質環境，密度不要太高，這有很多挑戰；填海方面，有共識維港不應再填。供應方面，我相信發展局盡辦法考慮不同措施，現在市建局可以考慮重建發展工廈，這個課題在政府內部討論了不少時間，若現時交由市建局做，可能工作速度及思維會有不同，這是一個好的提議。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201202/01/P201202010560.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201202%2F01%2FP201202010560.htm&d=ReI%2BzhX26GbyCeZBK3HxHWxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=ab1e25a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201202/01/P201202010560.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">樓價急升 下周破97歷史高位</span> 財司：必要時出手 不受換屆影響 2012/04/21<br />\n<br />\n樓價升勢未有放緩，反映二手樓價走勢的中原城市領先指數（CCL），最新報102.5點，按周升0.7%；計算指數滯後因素，料將突破97年10月高位102.93，創歷史新高。政府對樓價創新高，表示密切關注。<br />\n<a href=\"https://paper.hket.com/article/781837/%E6%A8%93%E5%83%B9%E6%80%A5%E5%8D%87%20%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E7%A0%B497%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E9%AB%98%E4%BD%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpaper.hket.com%2Farticle%2F781837%2F%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%2583%25B9%25E6%2580%25A5%25E5%258D%2587%2520%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%2591%25A8%25E7%25A0%25B497%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%258F%25B2%25E9%25AB%2598%25E4%25BD%258D&d=ReI%2BzhX26GbyCeZBK3HxHWxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=bb292d3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://paper.hket.com/article/781837/%E6%A8%93%E5%83%B9%E6%80%A5%E5%8D%87%20%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E7%A0%B497%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E9%AB%98%E4%BD%8D</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2013</div><br />\n《施政報告》全文（三）<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n52.　<span style=\"color: red;\">由於供應不足，樓價和租金大幅上升</span>，不少家庭被逼搬入較細或較舊單位，甚至搬入工廠大廈。今天，籠屋、板間房和劏房等蝸居成為數以萬計的香港居民無奈的選擇。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201301/16/P201301160281.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201301%2F16%2FP201301160281.htm&d=ReI%2BzhX26GbyCeZBK3HxHWxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=c00d7512\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201301/16/P201301160281.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2014</div><br />\n增加土地供應滿足住屋需求 發展局局長陳茂波<br />\n<br />\n有多位議員批評施政報告中的措施落實需要時間，未能夠解決目前的房屋問題，有一些甚至認為目前是畫餅充飢。我認為這些批評是罔顧事實和不公道的。施政報告中有關土地供應措施有短、中、長期，長期的措施如果我們現在不開始進行研究和規劃，日後便會像目前一樣，<span style=\"color: red;\">面對過去幾年供不應求的土地房屋供應，樓價飇升的困局是不能得到根本的解決。</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.news.gov.hk/tc/record/html/2014/02/20140213_200734.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Frecord%2Fhtml%2F2014%2F02%2F20140213_200734.shtml&d=ReI%2BzhX26GbyCeZBK3HxHWxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=372f28e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.news.gov.hk/tc/record/html/2014/02/20140213_200734.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2015</div><br />\n解決房屋問題需痛下決心 運輸及房屋局局長張炳良<br />\n（三）透過持續土地供應及實施需求管理措施以穩定樓市，並在私人住宅物業銷售和租務上促進良好做法。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2016</div><br />\n【樓市新辣招】<span style=\"color: red;\">上任4年樓價累升近4成</span>　梁政府被迫再出招壓市<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/52022/%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82%E6%96%B0%E8%BE%A3%E6%8B%9B-%E4%B8%8A%E4%BB%BB4%E5%B9%B4%E6%A8%93%E5%83%B9%E7%B4%AF%E5%8D%87%E8%BF%914%E6%88%90-%E6%A2%81%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E8%A2%AB%E8%BF%AB%E5%86%8D%E5%87%BA%E6%8B%9B%E5%A3%93%E5%B8%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F52022%2F%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%25BE%25A3%25E6%258B%259B-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E4%25BB%25BB4%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%2583%25B9%25E7%25B4%25AF%25E5%258D%2587%25E8%25BF%25914%25E6%2588%2590-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25BF%25AB%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%258B%259B%25E5%25A3%2593%25E5%25B8%2582&d=ReI%2BzhX26GbyCeZBK3HxHWxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=dec5244d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/52022/%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82%E6%96%B0%E8%BE%A3%E6%8B%9B-%E4%B8%8A%E4%BB%BB4%E5%B9%B4%E6%A8%93%E5%83%B9%E7%B4%AF%E5%8D%87%E8%BF%914%E6%88%90-%E6%A2%81%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E8%A2%AB%E8%BF%AB%E5%86%8D%E5%87%BA%E6%8B%9B%E5%A3%93%E5%B8%82</a><br />\n<br />\n鄭家純：辣招作用不大　政府干預唔係幾好<br />\n<br />\n要解決樓市根本問題、為樓價降溫，<span style=\"color: red;\">鄭家純認為需要從供應着手</span>，政府應盡量推出土地。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20161122/bkn-20161122122051307-1122_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20161122%2Fbkn-20161122122051307-1122_00842_001.html&d=ReI%2BzhX26GbyCeZBK3HxHWxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=88950669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20161122/bkn-20161122122051307-1122_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017</div><br />\n樓價乾升 十年計劃供應不足 4.3萬公營屋未有地<br />\n「熟地」用盡 達標極大挑戰 陳帆：土地令港人「非常痛」<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2017-12-21/43334582\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fnews%2F2017-12-21%2F43334582&d=ReI%2BzhX26GbyCeZBK3HxHWxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=3fa2b610\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2017-12-21/43334582</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2018</span></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭：樓價飊升治本方法必須增加土地供應</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府一路加 樓價一路跟住升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63127e5823b976a0f53c04d352d478d5f68e0443","tid":690756,"uid":7369,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:25:01.000Z","msg":"係呀, 拆鳩左個高爾夫球場咪大撚把地囉"},{"pid":"17a1853fd7c6be225f8f6f099afcdee05c5aef44","tid":690756,"uid":29314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:27:24.000Z","msg":"日日150件，點起樓都唔夠架啦"},{"pid":"07e725dbe8b611951fe21d7a017d26883790c73a","tid":690756,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:29:19.000Z","msg":"內文打錯咗，應該係<br />\n<br />\n樓價一路升，政府繼續同你講加土地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ador