bc004c9","tid":690756,"uid":6802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:40:17.000Z","msg":"明知香港土地係得丁屎咁多，就算再多樓價都係貴.<br />\n<br />\n增加土地只係一個長遠方法，由搵地賣地再起樓賣出都差唔多要5，6年既事.仲唔計你起出黎個d私人樓炒到貴一貴.樓價邊可能因為土地多咗就會唔升.根本增加土地只係一個單方面覺得會令樓價跌既方法."},{"pid":"3daa300fdaa26f00082fac2b9b9506cbd8c30f0a","tid":690756,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:40:26.000Z","msg":"開物業資產增值稅100%<br />\n根本就想炒埋一份"},{"pid":"cccab149d48e81a20274a22feecc8c09ec5accc4","tid":690756,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:42:16.000Z","msg":"唔夠位放大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4af107865f7da0ae1c56fa941e19f420fedcc0b5","tid":690756,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:43:05.000Z","msg":"依家巿場都hold 10萬單位<br />\n<br />\n起得多咪又hold起造巿"},{"pid":"af38f0949fee29dee51a85357b1a07b2dbedeb89","tid":690756,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:44:58.000Z","msg":"日日150之餘 <br />\n再加上奴才計劃 <br />\n當人戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b47a9ccf5d456ddbd5d7de2a912ca7b03f875ae7","tid":690756,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:45:46.000Z","msg":"見到隔離post屌政府問MTR拎地起公營屋<br />\n就知地產商根本無得輸<br />\n<br />\n從根本着手增加土地供應-&gt;比地產商買土地 <br />\n地產商賣貴樓-&gt;建成後,慢慢分幾次推出市場-&gt;推高樓價<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c83bfe399c14cc37483f9ef4173ef7231e623e","tid":690756,"uid":56321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:46:32.000Z","msg":"每日150人，唔截源頭嘥鳩氣"},{"pid":"c3abe2954f3e1b7a6e41442b4fb50f951ce1d1b7","tid":690756,"uid":37232,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:48:12.000Z","msg":"以地事蝗, 如抱薪救火, 薪不盡火不滅"},{"pid":"d7e1280d62d1863ae047e844c380dd91301e7b26"